&lt;p&gt;I regularly participate in national and international conferences related to &lt;strong&gt;text mining&lt;/strong&gt;, &lt;strong&gt;data science&lt;/strong&gt;, and &lt;strong&gt;statistical analysis of textual data&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Here are some recent highlights from my teaching and conference presentations:&lt;/p&gt;

